data.description: Located in the pines you will find this amazing custom home on 11 acres. Beautiful views, very quiet location.  Large decks on 2 sides, rebuilt less than 1 year ago..   The house is in excellent shape, It boasts a large living room with wood burner and pellet stove,  great kitchen and additional kitchen area in the large dining room .  It borders the BLM wilderness study area . 20 gall/min well and large storage tank ensures plenty of water. There is a small creek that holds water several times a year. Home, well and septic have been inspected in the last year. Roof was partially replaced.Floors are carpet, tile and wood. There are no covenants or restrictions. Real Estate Contract available with $49,000 down, balance at 6% over 30 years.  Also assumable VA loan of $225,000 at 4 1/4 %
